<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />的商店裡賣的樹苗，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都是在<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />買不到的，<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相當稀有喔～！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不愧是<delay8 />植物專家！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然樣樣精通是很好，<delay20 />
不過專注發展也很令人嚮往呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽說挖土種花<delay8 />可以療癒身心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道<colour id="3" /><delay8 />然然<colour id="65535" />他<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是因為每天弄花弄草，<delay8 />毫無壓力，<size value="100" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以個性才會那麼愜意自在嗎？！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如<delay20 />我也去<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />的商店<delay8 />
買下各種不同的幼苗和種子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />培養人見人愛的體質好了？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道嗎？<delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要把花朵並排種植，<delay8 />
不知不覺就會在附近開出新的花朵，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還有可能是罕見的顏色喔！
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是<colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />告訴我的，<delay20 />
好像叫做<delay8 />「配種」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，只要每天澆水就會發生！
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花朵們一定是<delay8 />感受到我們的愛，<delay20 />
所以用驚喜來報答我們！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用花朵做的飾品<delay8 />很可愛吧～<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然摘下來的瞬間<delay8 />
覺得有點可憐<tag a="110" b="0" />
不過，<delay20 /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠替像我這樣的時尚女孩打扮，<delay20 />
花朵一定也覺得如獲新生，
非常幸福吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道「地球日」嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是大家一起思考<delay8 />大自然重要性的日子喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了世上的植物，<delay20 />
我們才能呼吸新鮮空氣，保持健康，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後花朵還能襯托我<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我今天<delay20 />要帶著<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比平常更多的謝意，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為它們多澆點水～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>